# Upscale variant outputs. The interwheel-2x/-4x mounts under public/assets/
# are symlinks created on demand by scripts/interwheel/make-video.mjs and
# point into generated-assets/, so no trailing slash here (a trailing slash
# only matches directories, not symlinks).
public/assets/interwheel-2x
public/assets/interwheel-4x
public/assets/interwheel-4x-alpha-aa
# Stray top-level upscale variants (occasionally copied out of generated-assets
# while comparing models).
/animejanai-v3-compact-x2x2
/median-4x
remotion/node_modules/
# Per-run sources & dynamic assets copied into Remotion public/ by
# compose-short.mjs. Ignore everything except the .gitkeep placeholder.
remotion/public/latest/*
!remotion/public/latest/.gitkeep
# User-supplied source video for compose-wasted.mjs experiments. Big and
# per-machine — wasted.png/wasted.mp3 are tracked as canonical assets, the
# base video is whatever the user drops in.
/base.mp4
# Claude Code internal state (scheduled tasks, etc).
.claude/
